  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个部署流程的状态图，从初始状态开始，Developer应该是第一个参与的角色，他要同时对接Infrastructure和configMap这两个部分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Developer",
        "Infrastructure",
        "configMap"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Developer作为起点。那Infrastructure和configMap之间需要有关联吗？还是它们各自独立？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infrastructure",
        "configMap"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "它们有关联，Infrastructure要指向configMap，表示基础设施层会用到配置数据。然后configMap再流向Kubernetes，最后Kubernetes部署出Application。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infrastructure",
        "configMap",
        "Kubernetes",
        "Application"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我加上Infrastructure到configMap的连接，以及configMap→Kubernetes→Application的链路。Application作为终点吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infrastructure",
        "configMap",
        "Kubernetes",
        "Application"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Application连到终止状态。整个流程就是：开发者启动，协调基础设施和配置，配置进入K8s，最终产出应用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Application",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了，您看一下：起点到Developer，Developer分出两条线到Infrastructure和configMap，Infrastructure也指向configMap，然后configMap→Kubernetes→Application→终点。结构对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Developer",
        "Infrastructure",
        "configMap",
        "Kubernetes",
        "Application"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "Developer到configMap这条线我觉得方向可能需要调整——不对，等一下，方向是对的，但让我再确认下：是Developer指向configMap，表示开发者去创建或修改配置，对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Developer",
        "configMap"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，当前就是Developer指向configMap，表示开发者主动维护配置。整个图已经完整了，需要保存这个版本吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
